title: [Grawood Farmstead, Field]
description: This small segment of the field has been left empty, the dirt untouched and spotted with patches of grass.  From nearby, voices can be heard, and the canopies and banners of booths and tents fan out to occupy the remainder of the field's heart.
paths: Obvious paths: north, northeast, east, south, southwest, west
room.location: Grawood Farmstead outside of River's Rest
